message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as automatic question generation. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as AQG is a subfield of AI, "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as the proposed method uses a dual attention network, "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as the task involves retrieving information from a passage, and "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as the proposed method uses neural networks.
